<div class="container">
	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-md-4 col-md-offset-2">			

			<div class="well">
			
				<!-- step buttons -->
				<div class="row">
					<div class="col-md-4">
						<h2><span class="label <% if !cookies["last_poll"] %>label-warning<% else %>label-default<% end %>">Step 1</span></h2>
					</div>
					<div class="col-md-4">
						<h2><span class="label <% if cookies["last_poll"] && !cookies["mailed-" + cookies["last_poll"]] %>label-warning<% else %>label-default<% end %>">Step 2</span></h2>
					</div>
					<div class="col-md-4">
						<h2><span class="label <% if cookies["last_poll"] %><% if cookies["mailed-" + cookies["last_poll"]] %>label-warning<% else %>label-default<% end %><% end %>">Step 3</span></h2>
					</div>
				</div>
				<!-- end step buttons -->


				<% if !cookies["last_poll"] %>

					<%= render 'home/step1' %>

				<% elsif cookies["last_poll"] && !cookies["mailed-" + cookies["last_poll"]] %>
	
					<%= render 'home/step2' %>
	
				<% else %>

					<%= render 'home/step3' %>

				<% end %>
				
				
				</div><!-- end well -->

			</div>
			<div class="col-md-4">

				<div class="row">
					<div class="col-md-12">
						<h1>Do you need feedback?</h1>
						<p><div class="logo intext">POLLIFY</div> allows you to create <b>anonymous</b> and <b>simple</b> polls for all occasions.</p>
						<p><ul class="tick-list">
							<li>Get feedback on your project</li>
							<li>Get feedback on your classes or courses</li>
							<li>Anonymous</li>
							<li>Free</li>
							</ul>
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="row">
					<div class="col-md-12">

						<% if !cookies["last_poll"] %>
						<h2>Get started!</h2>
						<div class="row">
						<div class="col-md-2">
							<span class="arrow arrow-left"></span>
						</div>
						<div class="col-md-10">
							<p>Create your poll by filling out the form on the left.<p>
							<p>Create a PIN for users if you like. Protect your poll administration with a PIN as well.</p>
						</div>
						</div>
						<% elsif cookies["last_poll"] && !cookies["mailed-" + cookies["last_poll"]] %>
						<h2>Next step</h2>
						<div class="row">
						<div class="col-md-2">
							<span class="arrow arrow-left"></span>
						</div>
						<div class="col-md-10">
							<p>That was so easy! Now, send your new poll to everyone that you want to access it!</p>
						</div>
						</div>
						<% else %>
						<h2>Booom!</h2>
						<div class="row">
						<div class="col-md-12">
							<p>That's it, you're all setup! Now your friends, colleagues or lovers can vote and comment in your poll.</p>
						</div>
						</div>
						<% end %>
					</div>

				</div>

			</div>

		</div>
	</div>
